Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.59,0:00:09.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休息日的早上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.37,0:00:25.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.59,0:00:46.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由由  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.78,0:00:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宫  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.50,0:00:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一大早就这么伟大呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.34,0:00:52.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩服佩服
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.82,0:00:55.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只扫了一下门口结果扫到这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.56,0:00:58.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便而已  我想就一起扫了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.28,0:01:03.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也只有在休息天才能早起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.55,0:01:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果只睡在被窝里就太浪费时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.11,0:01:10.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是吉野屋老师
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.72,0:01:13.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.63,0:01:15.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.09,0:01:19.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦  宫子同学  由乃同学
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,---------------
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.90,0:02:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0}{\c&H404080&}「5月27日  狼狗怪兽」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.52,0:02:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想从车站开始就会有牌子了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.44,0:03:01.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且也没有那么远
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.37,0:03:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是不认识路了就打电话回来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.60,0:03:06.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.08,0:03:08.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个都要小心点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.41,0:03:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.65,0:03:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由由
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.53,0:03:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点快点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.94,0:03:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.14,0:03:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要拉扶手吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.58,0:03:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  没有关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.46,0:03:39.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在电车中斜着努力站好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.29,0:03:42.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉不管是竖的摇晃还是横的摇晃都比较容易站稳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.74,0:03:44.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要试试
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.00,0:03:50.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃大人  稍微蹲下一点会更加稳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.18,0:03:53.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.69,0:03:54.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.09,0:03:57.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请坐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.21,0:04:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天气这么好  真舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.34,0:04:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  晴空万里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.82,0:04:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是感谢吉野屋老师
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.03,0:04:10.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.61,0:04:16.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师  休息日也要去学校吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.92,0:04:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  昨天魔王打电话到我家里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.85,0:04:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被他叫出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.05,0:04:24.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔王
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.24,0:04:28.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  脸又细又长
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.97,0:04:32.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且接电话的是我的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.80,0:04:36.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两位今天要怎么度过
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.99,0:04:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期中考试也结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.62,0:04:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天还没有决定要做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.22,0:04:41.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.06,0:04:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.41,0:04:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就告诉你们最适合这个季节的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.66,0:04:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岩桦站附近有座很棒的神社哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.25,0:04:54.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便说下岩桦站
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.45,0:04:57.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是为了去见山吹高中的老同学才去的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.66,0:05:01.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班主任说在同一班级有两个非常合得来的同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.18,0:05:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他经常对我们说「你们两个真的很像呢」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.24,0:05:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班级里居然有两个吉野屋老师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.71,0:05:14.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岩桦站  岩桦站
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.41,0:05:19.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宫居然还记得神社的地址
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.63,0:05:22.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听了后面的话  意识都飞走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.25,0:05:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后面还说了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.74,0:05:36.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须要登这个楼梯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.94,0:05:38.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许会肌肉痛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.47,0:05:45.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由由
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.98,0:05:49.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来比赛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.79,0:05:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.95,0:05:55.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.02,0:05:58.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.46,0:06:11.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好长的楼梯  我已经累了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.71,0:06:14.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由由加油  现在只有一半哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.17,0:06:19.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加把油  刚才是450
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.46,0:06:25.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,451  452  453  454
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.70,0:06:28.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由由  现在几点了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.42,0:06:33.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在1点25分
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.59,0:06:42.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宫  太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.81,0:06:51.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.56,0:06:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  真是个不错的神社
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.04,0:06:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么马上开始…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.02,0:07:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  小姐们  来素描的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.57,0:07:03.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.45,0:07:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢画吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.12,0:07:06.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.63,0:07:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.16,0:07:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里有断坡  要小心一点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.50,0:07:13.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀  谢谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.74,0:07:15.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀  小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.50,0:07:19.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天又是晴朗的天气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.38,0:07:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  非常地舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.65,0:07:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道  吉野屋老师之所以说有个很棒的神社是因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.16,0:07:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你的是为了什么存在的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.17,0:07:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为了从不详之物手中保护神社吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.72,0:07:43.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过看上去却很弱的样子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.71,0:07:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要更加…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.32,0:07:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.72,0:07:54.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宫  那样的话谁都不会来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.84,0:07:59.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  到三点为止就自由行动吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.55,0:08:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.56,0:08:04.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不习惯在画画时被人看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.41,0:08:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.77,0:08:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.34,0:08:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.99,0:08:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉野屋老师一定是想让我们看这风景
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.46,0:08:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宫？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.07,0:08:37.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感觉刚才有谁看着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.71,0:08:40.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是错觉…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.20,0:08:46.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个那个  有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.94,0:08:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.64,0:08:51.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以收下那幅画吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.82,0:08:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你不嫌弃的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.64,0:08:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐真是天才
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.40,0:08:59.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.64,0:09:12.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.09,0:09:15.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以在这里看姐姐画吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.13,0:09:22.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.02,0:09:24.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.82,0:09:42.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易有一个休息日的说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.19,0:09:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我应该每次见到你都有叮嘱过到昨天为止要交出来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.00,0:09:49.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没能记住
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.35,0:09:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明知道必须要交出来的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.27,0:09:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不在还能赶上的时候着手工作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.79,0:09:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.96,0:10:12.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宫  久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.90,0:10:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  由由  画好了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.21,0:10:19.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  等回到房间后想再画一点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.53,0:10:22.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生了什么好事？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.16,0:10:27.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有发生那事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.82,0:10:30.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  表现地非常开心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.57,0:10:35.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那幅画里一定有她内心想诉说的什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.74,0:10:39.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  怎么会  只是风景画而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.74,0:10:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我想那孩子一定就是也到我那里去过的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.17,0:10:47.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有说想到我的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.35,0:11:02.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是风景画而已  我也没有画得那么好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.54,0:11:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是因为我的画  那孩子微笑了是真的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.79,0:11:19.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消息  是由乃发来的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.22,0:11:22.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？麹丘站？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.96,0:11:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？终点站？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.95,0:11:29.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宫子睡着了  由乃完全没有把报站内容听进去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.89,0:11:42.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直到终点站都没有发觉  到底发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.56,0:11:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在发呆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.54,0:11:47.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.97,0:11:51.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了  我马上就回房间继续素描
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.18,0:11:52.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.01,0:11:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我等下拿慰问品过去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.87,0:11:57.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  非常谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.46,0:12:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.41,0:12:08.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为笔的形状很可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.18,0:12:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不舍得去削  结果都没有怎么用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.01,0:12:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  有很多种类
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.03,0:12:16.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宫没有收集吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.27,0:12:20.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  因为太小了  马上就找不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.71,0:12:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且一点也擦不掉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.29,0:12:23.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.10,0:12:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果只流行到四年级而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.69,0:12:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由由？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.31,0:12:42.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果还是买太多点心了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.30,0:12:45.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我不是说过太多了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.88,0:12:49.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不在买之前更加全力的制止我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.52,0:12:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,房东姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.59,0:12:57.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.72,0:12:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.33,0:13:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好  知道这所公寓吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.01,0:13:05.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.02,0:13:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得是在这前面转弯的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.89,0:13:10.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank You
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.64,0:13:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.11,0:13:14.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打工
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.41,0:13:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打工？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.45,0:13:20.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我在拍公寓或者楼房的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.49,0:13:24.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  排好了  给你们拍张
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.08,0:13:26.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是公司的相机吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.40,0:13:29.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  真敏锐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.77,0:13:33.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了  今天还非要再拍三栋不可
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.19,0:13:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,房东姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.52,0:13:42.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  203房间好象没有上锁的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.23,0:13:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,锁？203？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.60,0:13:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.20,0:13:49.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没有什么可以偷的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.82,0:13:50.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.53,0:13:53.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  发生什么的话就…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.60,0:13:56.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  你太过担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.15,0:13:59.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是向阳庄而已  哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.29,0:14:01.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回见了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.84,0:14:02.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.55,0:14:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,房东姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.48,0:14:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么  你担心那个？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.43,0:14:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以打扰一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.16,0:14:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  请吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.82,0:14:21.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给  慰问品
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.54,0:14:36.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我买太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.39,0:14:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全没有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.99,0:14:42.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才遇到房东姐姐了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.39,0:14:46.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,房东姐姐？小宫有见过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.90,0:14:47.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.61,0:14:48.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.05,0:14:50.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么房东姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.15,0:14:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  来吃点心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.80,0:14:54.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给  奶油纳豆味的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.14,0:14:56.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个还没有吃过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.05,0:14:59.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弘学姐真是个挑战者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.99,0:15:02.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我完全无法想象味道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.99,0:15:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.06,0:15:10.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.34,0:15:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还粘粘的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.71,0:15:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.04,0:15:28.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  很让人回味
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.73,0:15:34.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  神社怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.26,0:15:37.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是个非常棒的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.98,0:15:39.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特别是神官爷爷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.64,0:15:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么神社怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.10,0:15:46.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上那个楼梯很辛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.83,0:15:50.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  一直到院内为止都要窒息了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.44,0:15:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是不好好给你按摩下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.53,0:15:55.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天可是要肌肉痛的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.76,0:15:58.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要肌肉痛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.85,0:16:02.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宫两格台阶一起跨  没有关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.30,0:16:03.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事没事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.68,0:16:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然怕楼梯很辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.41,0:16:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是相对的景色很漂亮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.29,0:16:08.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.08,0:16:11.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H4F4F4F&}来电：直居小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.09,0:16:13.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.32,0:16:15.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是担当打来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.74,0:16:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.96,0:16:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs25}是  是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.72,0:16:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs25}是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.53,0:16:30.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  这个是幸运巧克力哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.36,0:16:31.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的  我第一次看见
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.08,0:16:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.59,0:16:36.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然真的有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.34,0:16:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.65,0:16:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  如果有这个巧克力的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.10,0:16:42.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能和喜欢的人两情相悦哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.90,0:16:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由由  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.58,0:16:46.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  到底和谁…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.85,0:16:52.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  选了这个巧克力然后买的人是我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.56,0:16:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  这个算是谁的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.85,0:17:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就当没这回事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.14,0:17:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙英
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.50,0:17:22.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.46,0:17:25.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在社团活动才结束
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.15,0:17:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后偶然……
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.85,0:17:30.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊  是偶然  是偶然的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.86,0:17:33.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算不用说那么多次偶然我也知道的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.75,0:17:38.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道就好  那么贵安了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.69,0:17:42.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.97,0:17:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少也想给沙英看看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.93,0:17:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么不常出现的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.84,0:17:56.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说概率是5000颗中有1颗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.89,0:17:58.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再能遇见就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.79,0:18:00.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.21,0:18:02.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.71,0:18:05.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙英学姐真可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.70,0:18:06.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.43,0:18:08.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才出现了幸运巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.81,0:18:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  挺厉害的嘛  给我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.70,0:18:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃掉了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.36,0:18:15.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,融化掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.50,0:18:21.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我在下面碰到夏目了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.76,0:18:23.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  有说什么话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.20,0:18:27.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没有什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.08,0:18:28.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.52,0:18:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个奇怪的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.38,0:18:39.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.40,0:18:49.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桑原老师  怎么这么晚的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.78,0:18:51.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  到底发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.26,0:18:53.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  这是给老师的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.21,0:18:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是昨天应该提交的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.49,0:19:01.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  难得的一个休息日
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.54,0:19:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,校长他真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.84,0:19:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说要是今天里不交出来的话就不让我回去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.62,0:19:10.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  两个人一起做的话就快了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.52,0:19:18.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)}哎  难得一个休息日的说…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.89,0:19:30.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉野屋老师  你这个人真是越来越…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.12,0:19:35.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子已经饱饱的了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.39,0:19:38.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又陷到纳豆里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.57,0:19:39.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会再买过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.22,0:19:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚饭可以等下吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.63,0:19:44.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今晚也只吃果冻
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.85,0:19:48.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  弘学姐晚饭只吃果冻的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.57,0:19:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近一直都是这样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.55,0:19:52.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天吃果冻的话不会腻的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.06,0:19:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实是会的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.72,0:19:56.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才下了很多工夫哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.59,0:19:59.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在果冻上加些装饰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.82,0:20:02.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如炼乳  奶油
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.44,0:20:04.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且好多到扑出来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.29,0:20:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想如果浇那么多炼乳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.15,0:20:10.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就没有吃减肥果冻的意义了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.91,0:20:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还剩下很多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.03,0:20:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是不要了就给我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.55,0:20:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.70,0:20:20.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.12,0:20:23.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本就不需要放在心上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.32,0:20:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.55,0:20:25.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没有那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.51,0:20:29.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一想到马上就到换衣服的季节了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.58,0:20:30.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就郁闷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.24,0:20:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用减肥的人  我太羡慕了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.92,0:20:39.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个今天都素描了些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.12,0:20:41.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风景哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.38,0:20:42.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.91,0:20:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和小宫分别素描后
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.29,0:20:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又个小女孩过来  硬是问我要画
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.27,0:20:53.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对  那个女孩子也到我这里来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.89,0:20:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却没有硬要我的画
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.17,0:20:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然只是画到一半的画
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.33,0:21:01.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那孩子很高兴地收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.24,0:21:07.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想看看由由给她的画
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.36,0:21:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是给我看看女孩子没有心动的宫子的画吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.02,0:21:18.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宫画得真好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.67,0:21:19.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.17,0:21:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.51,0:21:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的画还没有画到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.64,0:21:30.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管如此  由乃的画中有什么打动了那孩子心的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.29,0:21:34.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃一定是画了极其美丽的画呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.76,0:21:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有那样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.53,0:21:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不管是什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.09,0:21:41.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要让人高兴了  就是很好的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.68,0:21:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天要是不肌肉痛就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.94,0:22:03.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许会有一天  我的画也能让人幸福吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.62,0:22:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.80,0:22:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0}5月27日  结束  待续
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,--------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.25,0:23:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冒昧地问一下  有谁吃过猫食吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.60,0:23:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.52,0:23:47.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有吃过  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.28,0:23:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我是想把这个成为小说的材料
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.40,0:23:51.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是我也没有吃过
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.21,0:23:53.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾  老师也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.53,0:23:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃过哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.37,0:23:55.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为完全没有味道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.51,0:23:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以稍微加点酱油的话味道还行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.63,0:23:58.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎哎～
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.45,0:24:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集「3月16日到23日  平静的金枪鱼风趣」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.87,0:24:06.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在向阳庄等着你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.31,0:24:07.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请务必要来看哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,----------------------------------------------------------
